Overview

Weather Predicter is a simple frontend application that displays current weather information using a public weather API. Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, it incorporates DevOps practices like version control with GitHub and automated deployment with Netlify.

Features

Fetch and display current weather data by city.

Show temperature, weather conditions, and relevant icons.

Responsive, clean user interface.

DevOps & Deployment

Git and GitHub for source control.

Automatic deployment to Netlify on every push to the main branch.

Lightweight CI/CD workflow.
